| Server | What it does |
|--------|--------------|
| **Playwright** | Browser automation (alternative to Puppeteer) |
| **Linear** | Project management (issues, cycles, projects) |
| **Jira** | Jira issue tracking |
| **Notion** | Read/write Notion pages and databases |
